Your StackOverflow notification inbox, right into your browser's toolbar.

- it checks for new notifications every minute
- shows a notification badge for new items
- supports all Stack Exchange websites

Source code now on Github: https://github.com/nuc-gr/StackNotify

----------------------------------------------------------------

Latest update: v0.3
- Better synchronisation. Items will be marked as read, only when the popup will be loaded.

----------------------------------------------------------------

v0.2.1

- Fixed badge count
- New items now have a different color

